name: Zillow Home Value Index (ZIP): Top Tier Homes - 74047
description: The Zillow Home Value Index is Zillow's estimate of the median market value of top tier homes within the zip code of 74047. Top tier homes are homes that fall into the top third of home values within the region. This data is calculated by Zillow Real Estate Research (www.zillow.com/research) using their database of 110 million homes.
